MSceneDetailViewModel.Name: Asahikawa
MSceneDetailViewModel.Phrase: Huff huff... I'm tired - I don't want to work anymore, that's enough.
We made our rounds in Sheep City. Most of the folks responded well to the lovely Asahikawa and the penguins she brought with her, and the mood was very welcoming.

MSceneDetailViewModel.Name: Asahikawa
MSceneDetailViewModel.Phrase: Mhm. Now we probably won't be attacked out of the blue.
You did a great job, Asahikawa. Thanks to you, it will be easier to conduct investigations in this city in the future.

MSceneDetailViewModel.Name: Asahikawa
MSceneDetailViewModel.Phrase: It's only on the women's side, though, only in Sheep City.
Even so, it made it much easier to carry out the mission. Good work, Asahikawa.

MSceneDetailViewModel.Name: Asahikawa
MSceneDetailViewModel.Phrase: Fufun, more praise♪

MSceneDetailViewModel.Name: Asahikawa
MSceneDetailViewModel.Phrase: I did what I had to do, no? I don't have to work anymore, no?
That's not going to happen. I want you to continue to work hard in cooperation with everyone else.

MSceneDetailViewModel.Name: Asahikawa
MSceneDetailViewModel.Phrase: Eeeeh～... I was going to do everything I had to do and then just laze around.
Why are you so unmotivated?

MSceneDetailViewModel.Name: Asahikawa
MSceneDetailViewModel.Phrase: A queen's job is simply to show her prestige. I don't work until sweat's on my Captain, it's against my policy.
Saying this, Asahikawa leapt into my chest. She started rubbing against me and asked for pampers.

MSceneDetailViewModel.Name: Asahikawa
MSceneDetailViewModel.Phrase: Got it? I've worked so hard, I'm not going to move again. Papa should hold me gently and pet me, like how you give Captainpats to a cute little critter.
Saying this selfishly, Asahikawa really stopped moving. For some reason, Pochy kept on staring at her.

MSceneDetailViewModel.Name: Asahikawa
MSceneDetailViewModel.Phrase: What? You have a problem?

MSceneDetailViewModel.Name: Pochy
MSceneDetailViewModel.Phrase: 'No... It's just that masculinity is frowned upon in this part of the city, so you preferably should not to use the word 'Papa'.'

MSceneDetailViewModel.Name: Asahikawa
MSceneDetailViewModel.Phrase: Fair enough. But, you know, Papa is Papa.
While Asahikawa and Pochy are having a strange exchange of opinions, everyone else is working energetically.

MSceneDetailViewModel.Name: Khajuraho
MSceneDetailViewModel.Phrase: Valentine's, it is the most precious ceremony of love in the world!

MSceneDetailViewModel.Name: Khajuraho
MSceneDetailViewModel.Phrase: Love and lovemaking! The liberation of the soul...!
Khajuraho is addressing the inhabitants of Sheep City with great joy, loudspeaker in her hand, which she retrieved from somewhere, somehow.

MSceneDetailViewModel.Name: Khajuraho
MSceneDetailViewModel.Phrase: Hey, do you think you're happy just by keeping the hated away? Do you think you're happy with that as long as the unpleasant ones are out of sight?

MSceneDetailViewModel.Name: Khajuraho
MSceneDetailViewModel.Phrase: No, right? Hey, can you hear me? I'm talking to you there! You, with your somewhat unfulfilled feelings!

MSceneDetailViewModel.Name: Khajuraho
MSceneDetailViewModel.Phrase: Hey, I'll fill that void in your heart! I'll show you how to fill that void!

MSceneDetailViewModel.Name: Khajuraho
MSceneDetailViewModel.Phrase: You may think I'm fooling you, just listen! I'm not asking you to believe me, just listen! Somewhere in your lonely heart, fill them with the words I have spoken!

MSceneDetailViewModel.Name: Khajuraho
MSceneDetailViewModel.Phrase: Someday, when you've forgotten, the moment you put them away, they'll come back to the surface! If it will lighten your heart even a little, what could be more wonderful than that!

MSceneDetailViewModel.Name: Khajuraho
MSceneDetailViewModel.Phrase: Hey, I want to fill you up! I want to make you happy!

MSceneDetailViewModel.Name: Khajuraho
MSceneDetailViewModel.Phrase: The moment you understand my feelings and listen to me - The first lovemaking will take place between you and me! That's the first step to happiness!

MSceneDetailViewModel.Name: Khajuraho
MSceneDetailViewModel.Phrase: Yes, thank you! Thank you for listening to me! I love you...♪

MSceneDetailViewModel.Name: Jeran
MSceneDetailViewModel.Phrase: ...What has Khajuraho been saying for a while now dah～? It's gibberish to Jeran dah～!

MSceneDetailViewModel.Name: Sentosa
MSceneDetailViewModel.Phrase: Don't take her too seriously, Jeran.

MSceneDetailViewModel.Name: Sentosa
MSceneDetailViewModel.Phrase: I don't know if it's magic or sorcery, but I felt a strange power in Khajuraho's voice. If you are a civilian that lacks defenses, just listening to that speech will take over your Captain and -

MSceneDetailViewModel.Name: Sentosa
MSceneDetailViewModel.Phrase: You'll be under Khajuraho's thumb as her slave. It's as if it's charm sorcery. She's not even a sorceress, so why is she able to do that?

MSceneDetailViewModel.Name: Jeran
MSceneDetailViewModel.Phrase: Khajuraho, seems that she was a very important person in the temple in his hometown dah～. So maybe she can do amazing things with that religion power lookalike.

MSceneDetailViewModel.Name: Sentosa
MSceneDetailViewModel.Phrase: Religion power... Well, it seems like 'that kind of thing' is her job. She's a preacher who goes around giving speeches in different places to increase her followers.

Yes, she is. She is a professional in that field. Our original mission to spread the culture of Valentine's Day in this region - Khajuraho, the preacher of love can accomplish this if we leave it to her.

MSceneDetailViewModel.Name: Sentosa
MSceneDetailViewModel.Phrase: Grrr... She's a shameless pervert who sexually harasses people all the time, yet she's more useful than Your Truly.

MSceneDetailViewModel.Name: Jeran
MSceneDetailViewModel.Phrase: Ahaha! That's true, Sentosa is just making a lot of noise at the moment dah～♪

MSceneDetailViewModel.Name: Sentosa
MSceneDetailViewModel.Phrase: You're not being very helpful either, Miss Jeran!?

MSceneDetailViewModel.Name: Khajuraho
MSceneDetailViewModel.Phrase: Hold it, hold it, don't make me work all the time, please?

MSceneDetailViewModel.Name: Asahikawa
MSceneDetailViewModel.Phrase: I did work though?

MSceneDetailViewModel.Name: Khajuraho
MSceneDetailViewModel.Phrase: Yes. Thanks to the celebrity Asahi's backing, my speeches are getting through. You're useful～, good, good♪

MSceneDetailViewModel.Name: Asahikawa
MSceneDetailViewModel.Phrase: Don't touch me. I did say Captainpats are fine, but no touching butts.

MSceneDetailViewModel.Name: Khajuraho
MSceneDetailViewModel.Phrase: It's fine, I'll caress your Captain then. With my technique, I can make any of your zones erogenous...♪

MSceneDetailViewModel.Name: Asahikawa
MSceneDetailViewModel.Phrase: Stay away from me.
Asahikawa hid behind my clothing, Khajuraho regretfully looked at her with a smile, then changed her attention to the other two.

MSceneDetailViewModel.Name: Khajuraho
MSceneDetailViewModel.Phrase: Heheh. If you want to be more useful than that, I have a job for you girls.

MSceneDetailViewModel.Name: Jeran
MSceneDetailViewModel.Phrase: For Jeran and her? What is it what is it? Jeran is useful dah～ Tigers are useful and the strongest dah～!

MSceneDetailViewModel.Name: Sentosa
MSceneDetailViewModel.Phrase: Yours Truly is far more useful! Lions are the strongest!

MSceneDetailViewModel.Name: Khajuraho
MSceneDetailViewModel.Phrase: Ahaha. Well then, will you help as my assistants?

MSceneDetailViewModel.Name: Jeran
MSceneDetailViewModel.Phrase: Khajuraho's?

MSceneDetailViewModel.Name: Khajuraho
MSceneDetailViewModel.Phrase: Yes. As you can see, I've been giving a speech for a while now-

MSceneDetailViewModel.Name: Khajuraho
MSceneDetailViewModel.Phrase: I want to put a bit more act into it, because people get bored if I just put a bunch of words together. I'm hoping you girls can help me with that♪

MSceneDetailViewModel.Name: Sentosa
MSceneDetailViewModel.Phrase: Act? What do you mean? What do Yours Truly and her have to do?

MSceneDetailViewModel.Name: Jeran
MSceneDetailViewModel.Phrase: Gaarrgh, Jeran doesn't really know anything else aside from destroying things dah～!

MSceneDetailViewModel.Name: Khajuraho
MSceneDetailViewModel.Phrase: It's fine. Anyone can do it, it's easy.
Khajuraho smiled glossily, stating as if it's a matter of fact.

MSceneDetailViewModel.Name: Khajuraho
MSceneDetailViewModel.Phrase: - You two, hug and kiss each other right now.
